message.entry: OBJ must be an interface object.
OBJ must be a 1-by-1 interface object.
The input argument A must be specified.
The third input argument must be a character vector or string.
PRECISION must be a character vector or string.
The input argument A must be numeric or a character vector or string.
Invalid PRECISION specified. Type ''instrhelp fwrite'' for more information.

FWRITE cannot be called. The FlowControl property is set to ''hardware'' and the Clear To Send (CTS) pin is low. This could indicate that the serial device may not be turned on, may not be connected, or does not use hardware handshaking.
